input_args.text: "Nah. Go take a nap. We love women, hate what they've become. Women are weaker than us, physically and emotionally, and easily misled. Thats why they have to be viciously protected. They're our life force, the exact opposite of an object. That's why it's so enervating to us when they concede to being just an object. Those ones have to go, and the men who objectify them."
